LEE MOKDAN CASE

36
00:03:07,896 --> 00:03:10,231
Do you remember the juvenile ghost case?

37
00:03:10,231 --> 00:03:11,733
- I do.
- It all began

38
00:03:11,733 --> 00:03:14,694
with this shaman who made that ghost.

39
