From 1958 to 2023.

94
00:06:07,533 --> 00:06:10,703
Do you think
there really is a serial killer...

95
00:06:12,205 --> 00:06:13,664
who murdered them all?

96
00:06:14,582 --> 00:06:15,917
There's a pattern.

97
